ns0:DescribedValueSet.ns0:Purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains interventions used for ventilator care.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who have had an intervention for ventilator care. Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the Intervention category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Include codes representing an encounter diagnosis related to ventilator care using the SNOMED CT code system.),(Exclusion Criteria: None.)
